data.description: Welcome home to this completely renovated gem! This 3 bedroom, 2 bath house is more than meets the eye. Inside, you'll find an incredible in-law's quarter with a private entrace. It's the perfect space for guests or even a potential rental opportunity. Step outside onto your beautiful patio, a wonderful spot to relax and enjoy the Florida sunshine. The spacious Florida room provides additional living space and is perfect for entertaining guests or creating a home office. The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring granite countertops, a kitchen breakfast bar, 42' cabinetry, and stainless-steel appliances. It's the ideal space to whip up delicious meals and create lasting memories with loved ones. Conveniently located near the 408, you'll have easy access to all the amenities Orlando has to offer, including shopping, restaurants, and theme parks. Don't miss your chance to call this stunning house your home. Contact us today to schedule a private showing! ***MOTIVATED SELLER***  New roof 2022 - A/C 2018 - Water heater 2022 - COMPLETELY RENOVATED
